{
  "text": "Nonfreeness of single-site subsystems of fermion lattice systems was studied in [CITATION_1] , following a similar study of correlations in (LDA+DMFT) tight-binding models of transition metal oxides [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "119294997",
